Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.11,0:46:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have any problems there.\NWhy? Because there isn't anybody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.04,0:46:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor is there any place to be.\N>> If you don't exist, and there's any
