Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.68,0:47:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness itself.\NSo did you say we have to stop now?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.31,0:47:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She said we have to stop now\N>> this afternoon. I thought we'll spend a
