Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.88,0:50:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,floating.\NAnd so you float with no struggle. You
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.28,0:50:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,stop struggling.\NIf you constantly surrender, what you're
