Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.04,0:51:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not moralistic but to be correct\Nand not correct. That which constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.72,0:51:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,chooses incorrectness no longer\Nsurvives.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.24,0:51:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So truth from falsehood is innate\Nbiologically anatomically and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.88,0:51:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,neurohysiologically.\NWithout it you wouldn't you can't live.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.83,0:51:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the question?\N>> Oh surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.20,0:52:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's it's it's the Beatles song Let It\NBe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.59,0:52:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right. Let it be. It\Ncalibrates extremely high. And I
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.88,0:52:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,remember when it came out, let it be.\NThe Stones quickly countered with Let It
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.16,0:52:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleed, didn't they?\NWell, if you calibrate Let It Be
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.88,0:52:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,compared to Let It Bleed, let's see what\Nthe Beatles song Let It Be. We have
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.48,0:52:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,permission to do let it be. Let it be is\Nover 480. 500
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.40,0:52:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,499\N500 499. Pretty damn high. Let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.00,0:52:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be. Uh\Nso the Beatles were quite areriodite and
