Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.64,0:52:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So surrendering means to\Nuh relinquish to God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.72,0:53:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh and it's the actually when you think\Nof it is the easiest thing in the world
