Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.35,0:53:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh you know as I say you know yang is\Nlike so and yin is like so to allow to
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.00,0:53:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,allow as yin is surrender\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.88,0:53:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,thy will oh lord not mine.\NIf God's will is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.72,0:53:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that it heals then it heals. If God's\Nwill is for it not to heal it won't
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.20,0:53:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,heal. So you can only do so much within\Na certain level and the rest is up to
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.48,0:53:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,divine providence\Nwhich a more sophisticated person
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.96,0:53:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,discerns has karmic trends\Nand therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.40,0:54:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what you think is a negative experience\Nmay well be the undoing of the of
